CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 12 reads: "Chattel Mortgage Department - Left row: Marcella Happ, Sarah Haywood, clerks, and John B. O'Connor, utility clerk. Right row: Mildred Russell and Edward B. Smith, clerks; Evelyn Kelly, typist."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of mortgage department of the Prothonotary office,  left row: Marcella Happ, Sarah Haywood, and John B. O'Connor;  right row: Mildred Russell, Edward B. Smith, and Evelyn Kelly
